Module com.malvi
Package p4_group_8_repo.Controllers

Class MainMenuController

java.lang.Object
p4_group_8_repo.Controllers.MainMenuController
public class MainMenuController
extends java.lang.Object
This class tells the Main class which scene to load depending on the button pressed in the main menu. Image Loader object is instantiated from here to load all the images in the game.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void exitGame()
    If Exit button pressed, confirm exit; if 'Ok' selected then exit, if 'Cancel' selected then close dialog box and stay in Main Menu.
    void highScore()
    If Highscore button pressed set scene to High Score Board.
    void instructions()
    If Instructions button pressed set scene to Instructions Board.
    void playGame()
    If Play Game button pressed set scene to Game Play.
